---
title: Caribbean Coconut & Veggie Curry with Pineapple Salsa & Jasmine Rice
description: Serve up the flavours of Caribbean cuisine in a colourful and exciting bowl! With fluffy jasmine rice and a creamy coconut curry loaded with all kinds of veggies, then topped off by a scattering of charred pineapple salsa, this bowl gets better with every bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-coconut-veggie-curry-55e2b4a7.jpg
